  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/ImageIO\/kCGImagePropertyIPTCSupplementalCategory\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:47:45Z\n---\n\n# kCGImagePropertyIPTCSupplementalCategory\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nA supplemental category.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet kCGImagePropertyIPTCSupplementalCategory: CFString\n```\n\n## Image Categorization\n\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCUrgency**: The urgency level.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCSubjectReference**: The subject.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCCategory**: The category.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCFixtureIdentifier**: A fixture identifier.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCKeywords**: Keywords relevant to the image.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCContentLocationCode**: The content location code.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCContentLocationName**: The content location name.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCEditStatus**: The edit status.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCEditorialUpdate**: An editorial update.\n- **kCGImagePropertyIPTCObjectCycle**: The editorial cycle (morning, evening, or both) of the image.\n\n",
